# Concepts

## Circular Economy

An economic model focused on reuse, recovery and regeneration of materials.

## Reverse Logistics

Movement of used materials from customers back to collection and processing points.

## Smart Green Cycle

A retail sustainability framework using behavioral incentives to encourage bag return and recycling.

## Customer Retention

Strategies designed to increase repeat customer visits and purchases.

## ESG

Environmental, Social and Governance performance indicators.
